column1:
1.) $SPY - Do or Die Zone, 571 Fib 61.5% (Aug 2024 - Jan 2025), election gap. Watch for $VIX response at DoD level
2.) $QQQ - Do or Die Zone, Fib 61.5% (Aug 2024 - Jan 2025), election gap. Questions where is the LoH(D) and will there be a LoH(W) ? 
3.) $PYPL - nice weekly hold at confluence (66.5-68), 6K begin to DCA roll down and out for Dec 19 2025 ~0.45 delta 
4.) $VIX - she gives and takes, insane IV crush across prems. If brace for full drawdown, another 50% on prems. Hedge or hold? 
5.) $TSLA - watching for equity 
6.) $MSFT - Fib 61% 404.6 (Sept 2023 - July 2024) and support (D), CL (W) 480ish 
7.) $BABA - looking for holds at the bottom of range, need good risk management since very gappy 
8.) $DIS - looking for puts at LoH(D)
9.) $AMZN - watch for TR play 
10.) $AMD - watch 105-106 breakout, look above and fails, CnH(D) handle forming, bullish divergence? 
11.) $ADBE - possible calls (tight TP) at bottom of range 
12.) $PLTR - ER gap
